blosxom4nagios
--------------

blosxom4nagios is a special-purpose blogging application (a 
bloglet!) used for capturing notifications from nagios and making 
them available via atom or rss feeds. It allows you to receive
and track nagios notifications via your RSS reader instead of
clogging up your mailbox.




# 'notify-by-rss' command definition
define command{
        command_name    notify-by-rss
        command_line    /var/log/nagios/blog/bin/blosxom-post -h '$HOSTNAME$' -g '$HOSTGROUPNAME$' -s '$SERVICEDESC$' -S '$SERVICEGROUPNAME$' -t '$SERVICESTATE$' -o '$SERVICEOUTPUT$' -c '$CONTACTNAME$' -d '$DATE$ $TIME$' /var/log/nagios/blog/posts
}



